<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>付费项目 · Arseeya</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c1f, #1a1a2e);
            color: #eee;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: #ddd;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            background: #e94560;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560, #667eea);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .projects-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .project-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .project-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
        .project-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .project-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #e94560;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .project-card p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #ccc;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(233,69,96,0.2);
            border: 1px solid #e94560;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #e94560;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e94560;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn-disabled {
            background: #555;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        .btn-disabled:hover {
            background: #555;
            transform: none;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #c5314b;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }
        footer a {
            color: #aaa;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        footer a:hover {
            color: #e94560;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .projects-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="index.html">首页</a>
        <a href="https://arseeya.github.io/novels/%E5%90%AC%E6%BD%AE%E4%BA%8B%E8%AE%B0/">作品</a>
        <a href="world.html">百科</a>
        <a href="download.html">下载</a>
        <a href="paid.html">付费项目</a>
    </div>

    <h1>💰 付费项目</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">支持作者 · 获取定制服务</div>

    <div class="projects-grid">
        <!-- 约稿卡片 -->
        <div class="project-card">
            <div class="project-icon">✍️</div>
            <h3>文章约稿</h3>
            <p>定制创作 · 专属故事</p>
            <div class="status-badge">⏳ 暂未开放</div>
            <div>
                <button class="btn btn-disabled" disabled>暂未开放</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 更多付费项目可在此添加 -->
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border-radius: 1rem; text-align: center;">
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaa;">📖 更多付费项目正在筹备中，敬请期待</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 0.5rem;">具体规则以《完整网站使用条款》第5条为准</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        © Arseeya. All Rights Reserved | <a href="terms.html">📜 完整条款</a>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
